# KHEPRA PROTOCOL - VERCEL ENVIRONMENT CONFIGURATION
# ==============================================================================
# IMPORT INSTRUCTIONS:
# 1. Go to Vercel Project Settings > Environment Variables
# 2. Click "Import .env" and select this file.
# 3. UPDATE the AGENT_URL value to your active tunnel.

# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# 1. FRONTEND CONNECTION (CRITICAL)
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# The URL of your local Agent tunnel (ngrok or Cloudflare Tunnel).
# This allows the Vercel UI to talk to your local "ERT" brain.
# EXAMPLE: https://friendly-monitor-123.ngrok-free.app
# NOTICE: Do NOT include a trailing slash (/)
AGENT_URL=https://agent.souhimbou.org

